{
  "stem": "14687.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I remember they used to give, every Sunday, you know, they used to give us some potatoes with cottage cheese-- three potatoes-- with the skin and the bread, and the cottage cheese.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we used to eat it, you know-- so happy it's Sunday-- every Sunday.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then after, we used to take off the skin, we used to eat the skin, because we were hungry.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then one day, one German Jewish, she knew that-- she ran away from the factory.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And for three days she was not there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when they were doing the appell, she was not there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They say, if they don't find her, they are going to kill 10 people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all of a sudden, they were looking, looking, looking.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she came back, because they caught her in this-- where she went.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they save us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they took her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They hit her so much in the head, in the body, the back black-- the head, they made it like [NON-ENGLISH], you know, all of these sores in there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all-- she was nearly dead in the-- in the floor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they say, all the Jews, we must hit her, and we must put cold water on top of her in buckets.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and we did this shame.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I thought she's going to finish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, after the war, when it was finished, and-- and we were there in the train coming home, we saw her alive.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I say, you so lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was about 45 years old that lady.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was an older lady.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But she was a German lady, Jewish, you see?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Where did you go from there?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
